{"tid":2435612,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李克強促備戰 憂美介入台海  軍費增6.8% 中國現不安","createTime":"2021-03-06T11:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T11:24:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c609f9d05d172c9bf3e4ca572442cf53dbc5d1ae","tid":2435612,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:21:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210306/WF6H7TBWKNGKDJGPGSOKHR2FCM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210306%2FWF6H7TBWKNGKDJGPGSOKHR2FCM%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=eace361a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210306%2FWF6H7TBWKNGKDJGPGSOKHR2FCM%2F&h=74ad273f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210306/WF6H7TBWKNGKDJGPGSOKHR2FCM/</a><br />\n<br />\n李克強促備戰 憂美介入台海 <br />\n軍費增6.8% 中國現不安<br />\n<br />\n【習權兩會】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：疫下基數低 復蘇勢破6<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】全國人大會議昨開幕，財政部發表政府預算草案，當中國防開支較去年增長6.8%，達1.35萬億元人民幣（下同，約1.62萬億港元），李克強在工作報告表示，要全面加強練兵備戰，統籌應對各領域安全風險，提高捍衞國家主權的戰略能力。政治學者對本報分析，軍費增幅增加表明中國對周邊的不安，需持續擴軍備戰；軍事專家則指，強軍主要目標是台海及會介入的美軍，他相信今年提出的軍費比實際開支少，存在「隱性軍費」。<br />\n<br />\n財政部在李克強發表報告後，發佈。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「急港緩台」兩岸求穩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s8yKdr6XbbjFayoERr70ysFVBRQ=/3150x2100/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UJWORME2DZFC5IF7CVFAK55MHE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs8yKdr6XbbjFayoERr70ysFVBRQ%3D%2F3150x2100%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUJWORME2DZFC5IF7CVFAK55MHE.jpg&h=ada46c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中國軍費年年增加引起西方國家關注；圖為天安門廣場閱兵展示的坦克。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「維穩費」支出2,210億<br />\n<br />\n至於俗稱「維穩費」的公共安全支出是1,850億元（約2,210億港元），增長0.7%。中國在2018年公佈的軍費增長率為8.1%，但2019年開。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李克強在工作報告中指出，過去一年國防和軍隊建設取得新的重大成就，在維護國家。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李克強提到，過去五年「十三五」（2016年至2020年）的國防和軍隊建設水。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政治學者吳強表示，軍費增長6.8%，高於去年的6.6%，總體上表明中國對周。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/konp4dgvk9qicEzTQ7VEmznyzcM=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7JFLAAIANRG3DARFP45G353CVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fkonp4dgvk9qicEzTQ7VEmznyzcM%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7JFLAAIANRG3DARFP45G353CVY.jpg&h=47c75b76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大陸軍機近年頻頻大舉越界，恫嚇台灣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uGDrubh3gGHWKX2rfiZ6Kmu22Mw=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YO5264Z2XVEWRPVP74HKZ3V7EY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuGDrubh3gGHWKX2rfiZ6Kmu22Mw%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYO5264Z2XVEWRPVP74HKZ3V7EY.jpg&h=baf832f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年美國尼米茲號與印度維克拉姆帝亞號聯合軍演，劍指中國。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iwU0koiztd0xqddtwF9a7BtPn_M=/1263x777/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DRUKVWEV6VBFLMYM7NFXL4KP7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiwU0koiztd0xqddtwF9a7BtPn_M%3D%2F1263x777%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDRUKVWEV6VBFLMYM7NFXL4KP7U.jpg&h=db08c18f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另撥隱性軍費搞閱兵<br />\n<br />\n軍事專家黃東則表示，今年公佈的軍費增長率比他預期低，他之前估計可能會有8%。他說，目前中國四面樹敵，但主要的軍費增長。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n黃東認為，就像以往一樣，中國公佈的軍費並不是一個真實數字，極可能存在「隱性軍費。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"e63c2671adea50b3a51add34c5a8dcfd6a0ef5e6","tid":2435612,"uid":46966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又可以貪多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f489c636fc7f8542bcc23f37d05be473a00343","tid":2435612,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T11:24:17.000Z","msg":"美帝又玩軍備競賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n橋唔怕舊總有傻閪"}]}